{"tid":1982931,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【頭條】負油價震驚網民　連登仔發現燈神媽咪麵月中睇好：代表作燈到負數","createTime":"2020-04-21T13:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T16:51:19.000Z","uid":66271,"like":79,"dislike":70,"uniUserReply":69,"replies":[{"pid":"a2d68db46cda3fc6c04d3730fdfdd93c69dff98c","tid":1982931,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329247624047759360.jpeg/LAkF4l_6TYhIMW2X9YWlVQlkgsvpsWFxB7MEigezBIo?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329247624047759360.jpeg%2FLAkF4l_6TYhIMW2X9YWlVQlkgsvpsWFxB7MEigezBIo%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=bf26a3ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n油價出現前所未見的黑天鵝大跌！昨晚紐約5月期油歷史性首次出現負價格，購買原油竟然有錢收，令不少人都難以置信。事件引來網民們熱烈討論，更有人笑指自己近月見證不少經濟大事，比長者們更有見識，有資格諷刺他們未見過風浪，「我3個月見識已經係佢地嘅70年見識」。<br />\n<br />\n新冠肺炎疫情下，環球經濟疲弱令原油需求暴跌，油價近月跌跌不休。昨晚紐約5月期油收報負37.63美元，大跌超過300%，原因之一是原油儲存設施已見爆滿，生產商寧願以負價格賣走原油，另外一個原因是原油結算日期已到，如果不平倉就會收到實物，於是被迫以低價平倉，而ETF需要轉倉至下月期油亦令跌勢加劇。<br />\n<br />\n油價歷史性負數令不少網民都熱烈討論，有人引述近月來美股從高位快速回落，兩星期內已經4度熔斷，甚至出現根本沒有人想像過的負油價，笑指就算有七、八十歲的長者其實「未見過風浪」，今年只玩3個月美股已經可以「看破紅塵」，「我3個月見識已經係佢地嘅70年見識」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外亦有網民翻舊帳，說原來在10日前（即4月11日）連登討論區股海明燈「媽咪麵」（麵神）曾經看好油價，更問三大油公司股票及與油價相關的交易買賣基金F三星原油期（3175）哪個較值得買入。媽咪麵出Po後油價一度上升，令網民以為麵神破燈，直至昨晚才知道媽咪麵燈力無窮無盡，成功將期油燈至負數。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246946567000064.jpeg/J85C-t9xtVGb9dTtIACcLccFyihxGeD4Vwewh1cHsIc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246946567000064.jpeg%2FJ85C-t9xtVGb9dTtIACcLccFyihxGeD4Vwewh1cHsIc&h=d46005cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246948676734976.jpeg/_s6ALIrU6xwQNCixi7pR3J0am8UH_hS-5h7zfeYe830\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246948676734976.jpeg%2F_s6ALIrU6xwQNCixi7pR3J0am8UH_hS-5h7zfeYe830&h=df86e718&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246950912299009.jpeg/jOWHw_dFHO212xaM9C02gay_rJ1AXvBue8IxinvCMYo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246950912299009.jpeg%2FjOWHw_dFHO212xaM9C02gay_rJ1AXvBue8IxinvCMYo&h=e6d0dcad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246952703266816.jpeg/XTb3lK1qCLik2rglw8hHXCYKndZVIzOhrE6XfaxOl30\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246952703266816.jpeg%2FXTb3lK1qCLik2rglw8hHXCYKndZVIzOhrE6XfaxOl30&h=5b19b227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246954573926400.jpeg/cIO-28RFDGhFbfR7zJ17Za5ju55kmpJzPGxs8zxsbPM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246954573926400.jpeg%2FcIO-28RFDGhFbfR7zJ17Za5ju55kmpJzPGxs8zxsbPM&h=6817383e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200421/329246956402642944.jpeg/AEwDrdPGBl1F18W5pcDcPkZJuXSs-TPsv2NG7r9jRu4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200421%2F329246956402642944.jpeg%2FAEwDrdPGBl1F18W5pcDcPkZJuXSs-TPsv2NG7r9jRu4&h=26649f47&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n彭博於4月7日曾報道，指有交易員購入1000張價格為0.5美元的原油期貨沽貨期權，交易額為1萬美元。報道認為，多國產油商減產令原油價格下跌至個位數的可能性變低，「近期原油價格波幅之大，這一張0.5美元的期權交易合約似乎是一張對沖全球需求下降的彩票」。<br />\n<br />\n截止今（21日）12時，5月期油價格已經大幅回升超過一倍至1.36美元，雖然重回正數，但仍然處於低水平的價格。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/463385/%E8%B2%A0%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E7%87%88%E7%A5%9E%E5%AA%BD%E5%92%AA%E9%BA%B5%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E7%9D%87%E5%A5%BD-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%87%88%E5%88%B0%E8%B2%A0%E6%95%B8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F463385%2F%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E6%25B2%25B9%25E5%2583%25B9%25E9%259C%2587%25E9%25A9%259A%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E9%2580%25A3%25E7%2599%25BB%25E4%25BB%2594%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E7%2587%2588%25E7%25A5%259E%25E5%25AA%25BD%25E5%2592%25AA%25E9%25BA%25B5%25E6%259C%2588%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%259D%2587%25E5%25A5%25BD-%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E4%25BD%259C%25E7%2587%2588%25E5%2588%25B0%25E8%25B2%25A0%25E6%2595%25B8&d=ncMleFGONnlHWKA8FqKBiZnDkpC49KclrNwegNic%2Fqo%3D&h=4a11eec5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/463385/%E8%B2%A0%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E9%9C%87%E9%A9%9A%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E9%80%A3%E7%99%BB%E4%BB%94%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E7%87%88%E7%A5%9E%E5%AA%BD%E5%92%AA%E9%BA%B5%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%AD%E7%9D%87%E5%A5%BD-%E4%BB%A3%E8%A1%A8%E4%BD%9C%E7%87%88%E5%88%B0%E8%B2%A0%E6%95%B8</a>"},{"pid":"801edd25e3da1bbda9d79e7d76b7aefb203fad67","tid":1982931,"uid":170395,"like":168,"dislike":1,"score":167,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:13:10.000Z","msg":"垃圾01"},{"pid":"cb2a9262e8149a64a0d2df6fa10e0c54561a7e84","tid":1982931,"uid":66271,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"媽咪麵有咩想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c64e57180d8e024dcd5bfe256f6bd01ad4367cb9","tid":1982931,"uid":177089,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"cb2a9262e8149a64a0d2df6fa10e0c54561a7e84","tid":1982931,"uid":66271,"like":45,"dislike":3,"score":42,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T13:13:53.000Z","msg":"媽咪麵有咩想講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci